properties.areaDesc: Lake Superior west of a line from Saxon Harbor WI to Grand Portage MN beyond 5NM
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 15 at 9:55AM EST until February 16 at 1:00AM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and waves
4 to 7 feet occurring.

* WHERE...Lake Superior west of a line from Saxon Harbor WI to
Grand Portage MN beyond 5NM.

* WHEN...Until 1 AM EST /midnight CST/ Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 AM EST /MIDNIGHT CST/ SUNDAY
